short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open new tab to Google search selected text combined with predefine keywords.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When you need to Google a lots of keyworks with the same prefix, this extension here to help you.
Example when you are reading One Piece, you may want to search "One Piece Sanji", "One Piece Chopper", "One Piece abc",... you can just select "Sanji"/"Chopper" and right click to seach. This tool will fill "One Piece" for you.
